{
  "stem": "24212.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She could steal that you wouldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She would steal the eyes out of your face and potatoes and whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I told her how to find me after the war-- two of them were-- three of us were so young, but I was the grown up youngster, and they were the kid youngsters.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the other one, this Yugoslav girl, was an intelligent girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she remembered you know, the university address in Prague.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she wrote to me, and ever since we are in touch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she was here, and I was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this other one, this Romanian, pshew, disappeared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I hope that she found some family, or I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left Auschwitz on my birthday in 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the rea-- that was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They always asked for volunteers-- which is sort of [LAUGHS] strange thing in Auschwitz, ask prisoners for volunteers-- for volunteers to work in a gardening outfit or in a candy factory, you know, all the goodies.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course we didn't believe what they are saying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Auschwitz whatever you volunteered for was 50%, the other 50 being the chimney, you know, weeding out for the chimney.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So then I said, if they will ask for volunteers, for volunteers on my birthday, I will volunteer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I figured few people die on their birthdays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then came, again, volunteers, we need volunteers for textile factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My birthday, I volunteer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with me, our appel roll, and some-- a whole bunch of us volunteered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we won.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The 50 went out of Auschwitz rather than up the chimney.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But could have gone any, any other way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's how I got marched out of Auschwitz gloriously.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
